          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "Cook pasta in heavily salted water according to instructions on pack but reduce cooking time by 3 mins. When the pasta is 3 min from being ready, add all the broccoli. Cook for 3 further mins and then drain, reserving the pasta water (KEY)."
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "a4a6df42-2faa-4fb4-8c2e-cc73b605f547",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "In the meantime, heat the oil over high heat, add the chicken and cook for about 5 mins (not fully cooked), add salt and pepper."
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "99a58a0e-bdac-4794-b009-96fd745f3279",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "Add the ricotta, pesto to a beaker and add about 200ml drained pasta water and mix."
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "d622130c-0dfc-462e-accd-8fe582eda557",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "Combine the pasta, broccoli, chicken, cherry tomatoes and ricotta-pesto sauce to a large oven tray, and mix. Cover with as much salt and pepper as desired and place in the oven for 15-20 mins until the top is crispy and the chicken is cooked through."
        },
